2 SECTION 5. Arkansas Code § 27-22-202(4), concerning the definition of
3 "insurer" used under the Arkansas Online Insurance Verification System Act,
4 is amended to read as follows:
5 (4) "Insurer" means a motor vehicle insurance company licensed
